libs.content:
find_library(hwloc_hwloc_library
	names hwloc
	hints ${hwloc_dir}
	path_suffixes lib lib32 lib64)

find_library(
    fftw_lib
    names "fftw3"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(
    fftwf_lib
    names "fftw3f"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(
    fftwl_lib
    names "fftw3l"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(adolc_libraries 
  adolc 
  paths $env{adolcdir} ${lib_install_dir} 
  path_suffixes lib lib64)

find_library(computecpp_runtime_library
  names computecpp computecpp_vs2015
  hints $env{computecpp_dir}
  path_suffixes lib
  doc "computecpp runtime library")

find_library(computecpp_runtime_library_debug
  names computecpp_d computecpp computecpp_vs2015_d
  hints $env{computecpp_dir}
  path_suffixes lib
  doc "computecpp debug runtime library")

find_program(computecpp_info_executable computecpp_info
  hints $env{computecpp_host_dir}
  path_suffixes bin
  no_system_environment_path)

find_library(metis_metis_library
      names metis
      hints ${metis_dir}
      path_suffixes lib lib32 lib64)

find_library(gsl_gsl_library
    names libgsl.dll.a gsl libgsl
    paths  ${gsl_possible_root_dirs}
    path_suffixes lib
    doc "gsl library" )

find_library(gsl_gslcblas_library
    names libgslcblas.dll.a gslcblas libgslcblas
    paths  ${gsl_possible_root_dirs}
    path_suffixes lib
    doc "gsl cblas library dir" )

find_library( bolt_library_static_release
        names libclbolt.runtime.gcc.a
        hints
            ${bolt_root}
            env bolt_root
        doc "bolt static library path"
        path_suffixes lib
    )

find_library( bolt_library_static_debug
        names libclbolt.runtime.gcc.debug.a
        hints
            ${bolt_root}
            env bolt_root
        doc "bolt static library path"
        path_suffixes lib
    )

find_library(tbb_library tbb hints ${_tbb_library_dir}
        paths env library_path env ld_library_path)

find_library(tbb_malloc_library tbbmalloc hints ${_tbb_library_dir}
        paths env library_path env ld_library_path)

find_library(tbb_library_debug tbb_debug hints ${_tbb_library_dir}
        paths env library_path env ld_library_path)

find_library(tbb_malloc_library_debug tbbmalloc_debug hints ${_tbb_library_dir}
        paths env library_path env ld_library_path)
find_library(opencl_libraries opencl doc "opencl lib for osx")

find_package(qt4 required components qtcore qtgui qtopengl)
